Skills.Name: Lantern Sparklers
Skills.Description: Raises own DEF by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Shields DMG ({1}% of skill user's ATK) of all allies (behind self) for 15s. Further shields DMG ({3}% of skill user's ATK) multiplied by total Bleed (Stacked) on all characters in battle for 15s. (Max. {4}%)
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises own DEF. Shields DMG of all allies behind self. Further shields DMG based on total Bleed effect(s) in battle

Skills.Name: Gleeful Goldfish
Skills.Description: Raises ATK of all Green Elemental allies based on total Bleed (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s (Max. {2}%). Further raises Speed based on total Bleed (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by <color=red>{4}%</color> for 10s. (Max. {5}%)
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises ATK and Speed of all Green Elemental allies based on total Bleed effect(s) in battle

Skills.Name: Beautiful, No?
Skills.Description: Raises DMG Received for all enemies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Further lowers DEF based on total Bleed (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by {2}% for 10s if Yellow Elemental (Max. {3}%). Inflicts 10x Bleed ({4}% of skill user's ATK) on self for 20s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises DMG Received for all enemies, lowers DEF based on total Bleed effect(s) in battle if Yellow Elemental. Inflicts Bleed on self

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Reduces DMG Received for all allies by <color=red>5.00%-40.00%</color> for 5s according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Summer Night Bloom
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, shields DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of self for 15s. Also raises Overheal by <color=red>{1}%</color> (Permanent). Also grants Blood Heal (Permanent). Further grants Nullify Bleed Removal. (Permanent)
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, shields DMG, raises Overheal, grants Blood Heal and Nullify Bleed Removal on self
